The 3 farest FACES of the MIN-MAX coordinate HEXAHEDRON
will be drawn and completed with the options:

0: NO DRAWING
   Suppress this type of drawings

1: Only 8 GLOBAL EDGES are drawn

2: QUADRILATERAL GRIDS
   The 3 faces are drawn with quadrilateral grids
   without background color

3: BACKGROUND of 3 FACES has the same color

4: CHESS-BOARD with 2 COLORS on the 3 FACES
   The 3 faces are drawn with quadrangles of alternated colors
   The edge greatest length is cut into 10 + 2 margins
   The 2 other dimensions are adjusted to an integer number
